:43:12.415Z", "title": "Image 8 of The Washington times (Washington [D.C.]), January 2, 1921, (FINAL EDITION)", "type": ["segment"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?sp=8"}], "timestamp": 1784397815127, "title_url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn84026749", "type": "zoom", "viewer_pagination": {"current": 8, "first": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1", "from": 8, "last": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=10", "next": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=9", "of": 44, "page_list": [{"number": 1, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1"}, {"number": "...", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=5"}, {"number": 6, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=6"}, {"number": 7, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=7"}, {"number": 8, "url": null}, {"number": 9, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=9"}, {"number": 10, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=10"}], "perpage": 1, "perpage_options": [25, 50, 100, 150], "previous": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=7", "results": "8 - 8", "to": 8, "total": 44}, "views": {"brief": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&st=brief", "current": "single", "epub": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&st=pdf", "gallery": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1&st=gallery", "grid": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1&st=grid", "image": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&st=image", "list": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84026749/1921-01-02/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1&st=list", "pdf": "https://www.loc.gov/resource